{
  "texts": [
    "In the preprocessing phase, three main methods are applied.",
    "These methods are image resizing followed by data oversampling and data augmentation.",
    "First, the original images are resized to 299 × 299 × 3.",
    "Then, the random oversampling method is applied to tackle the class imbalance problem.",
    "Then, to reduce the overfitting issue and improve the InceptionV3 deep learning architecture's generalization capability, data augmentation techniques are applied."
  ]
}